Package org.ietf.nea.pb.batch

IETF TNCCS message batch implementation.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PbBatchHeaderBuilder
    Generic builder to build a TNCCS batch header compliant to RFC 5793.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultTnccsBatchContainer
    Default helper object to pass on a TNCCS message batch and minor validation errors after parsing for further processing.
    PbBatch
    IETF RFC 5793 TNCCS batch.
    PbBatchFactoryIetf
    Factory utility to create a IETF RFC 5793 compliant TNCCS message batch.
    PbBatchHeader
    IETF RFC 5793 TNCCS batch header.
    PbBatchHeaderBuilderIetf
    Builder to build a TNCCS batch header compliant to RFC 5793.
